{"tid":653401,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖睇睇]17-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第33輪投選專區 #文詠珊 陳法拉 沈卓盈 岑麗香 袁澧林 陳嘉寶","createTime":"2018-05-04T16:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T17:19:38.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1750ad3c5eb9d6dca35854d42a711cbb0b3db8e","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:30am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n沈卓盈v黃翠如<br />\n鄧麗欣v劉佩玥<br />\n麥美恩v林泳淘<br />\n陳嘉寶v莊錠欣<br />\n文詠珊v彭慧中<br />\n陳煒v簡幗儀<br />\n孫慧雪v黃心美<br />\n黃心穎v岑麗香<br />\n袁澧林v陳法拉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冠聯第三十二輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5lnQsr0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5lnQsr0.png&h=6b303a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=LiGpq4PHcy29c2DU02GkFwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7aa35180\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a2f9157e540ecfe4615f1ba49f16492d922ebb","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":118,"dislike":27,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第三十三輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-5 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EHEZ1xx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEHEZ1xx.png&h=4d03d4c0&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s4d4gFG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs4d4gFG.png&h=b17b988a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(3)沈卓盈vs黃翠如(10)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"43ca73162849e10a5e14d2fc48fd8d04bc4ea76f","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":115,"dislike":29,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-5 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/n3aLUhb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fn3aLUhb.png&h=56a17145&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/007iIPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F007iIPg.png&h=c3ed5227&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(7)鄧麗欣vs劉佩玥(15)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"c9bcb2d38b3184d45aef6a0965d48afe08ca9129","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":28,"dislike":98,"score":-70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018