:"樓下仲有袁澧林對陳法拉,好緊張呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">最後一輪冠軍聯賽賽程:<br />\n<br />\n34.<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-12<br />\n黃心美v陳嘉寶<br />\n彭慧中v黃心穎<br />\n岑麗香v鄧麗欣<br />\n陳法拉v麥美恩<br />\n劉佩玥v孫慧雪<br />\n莊錠欣v沈卓盈<br />\n簡幗儀v袁澧林<br />\n黃翠如v文詠珊<br />\n林泳淘v陳煒<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ecf324ebb0249a67e528570c4d18930d129c4f3c","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":33,"dislike":106,"score":-73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-5 12:46am-10:46pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rYeiDIq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrYeiDIq.png&h=75553268&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a09GUCK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa09GUCK.png&h=423467c8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(5)袁澧林vs陳法拉(2)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"2b4fbb29da49ecde0121983abc55d64e6254c6b0","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:47:22.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半季籌到既296元已經捐出,多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽已於4月29日舉行<br />\n冠軍由李佳芯奪得<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃決賽 5月27日凌晨0時<br />\n新垣結衣(日本)<br />\nvs<br />\nIU(韓國)<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲打們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3c77a3d9ed679f23e855ea71bde48b0077cf9b","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbf836b4d3a99c31c6c4e70e5bb27b76f47af98","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fa7e19df31cd1426a36c08e52a2fd900c11679","tid":653401,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5010240aa0cf6f3370938d35a16a4da8197b30","tid":653401,"uid":29549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5adfd4431341fd0a22bdd8e52f1d3ce3b5290a67","tid":653401,"uid":152759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:35:04.000Z","msg":"袁澧林收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd30679665e97d0eec3909bb88cf25767bc496a7","tid":653401,"uid":7375,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:42:41.000Z",